<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.4">
<l>orumakaḷ taṉṉai yuṭaiyē ṉulakam niṟainta pukaḻāl</l>
<l>tirumakaḷ pōla vaḷarttēṉ ceṅkaṇmāl tāṉkoṇṭu pōṉāṉ</l>
<l>perumaka ḷāykkuṭi vāḻntu perumpiḷḷai peṟṟava cōtai</l>
<l>marumaka ḷaikkaṇṭu kantu maṇāṭṭup puṟañceyyuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have one daughter. I raised [her] like the lady Tiru [herself],</l>
<l rend="indent">with praise that filled the world.</l>
<l>Red-eyed Māl took her and left.</l>
<l>Yaśodā who, being the great lady living with the clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">begot that great boy,</l>
<l>joyfully seeing [her] daughter-in-law,</l>
<l rend="indent">will cherish [this] bride,</l>
<l>won’t she?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
